reviews.review:
This game is great;

This game is amazing it has a lot of potential and has an amazing skill base. 

However:

The game has a lot of work though needed done. Ever since the game was made free to play it has brought in a ton of hackers and has ever since made matchmaking really difficult. I have owned this game for a fair while; before cheaters were really popular. The game was fairly good at keeping cheaters out of competitive matchmaking and allowed for the game to be really enjoyable. The game now is mainly full of cheaters and that is why I am not personally recommending it unless you are not going to play competitively. 

Don't get me wrong this game is amazing but ever since Valve decided to make the game free it has been ruined. The Anti-Cheat system is terrible and allows for pretty much anyone, anywhere to cheat. The cheaters are out of control now, even though Prime has been added (to try and stop the cheaters by making you ether grind to level 21 or to pay 20.95 AUD) it still doesn't help due to there being ways to bypass it. The game is pretty much impossible to gain high rankings now due to the cheaters. 

Overall; 

The game is free and you can always try it. The reason I'm not recommending is due to the lack of support and work done to prevent cheaters. Overall the game is heaps fun and I do recommend you try it. 

Let me know if you have played it and want you think;
